Market Analysis and Insights

Global Display Unit in Vehicle Infotainment Market

Data Bridge Market Research analyses that the display unit in vehicle infotainment market would exhibit a CAGR of 10.80% for the forecast period.

Information and entertainment are provided through embedded infotainment systems, which are a novel technology in the entertainment sector. In-vehicle infotainment systems are infotainment systems that are incorporated in automobiles. In automobiles and commercial vehicles, these systems improve the driving experience. This system is often a two-way communication device with a variety of audio and visual capabilities.

The upsurge in demand of navigation services, entertainment and security services will influence the growth rate of display unit in vehicle infotainment market during the forecast period of 2022-2029. The display unit in vehicle infotainment market is likely to grow significantly due to the rising utilization of cloud technologies. Also, increasing preferences towards rear seat entertainment is a contributing factor to the growth rate of display unit in vehicle infotainment market. Furthermore, rise in infrastructure development and surging industrialization are the major market drivers that will have positive impact on the market’s growth rate. Some of the factors such as upsurge in the level of disposable income, rising urbanization and technological advancement will further propel the market’s growth rate. The rising growth of smartphone industry and strong demand from various end-use industries are the major drivers that will further cushion the growth of display unit in vehicle infotainment market.

Moreover, upsurge in the adoption rate of smart technologies such as 5G and artificial intelligence will carve the beneficial opportunities for the growth of display unit in vehicle infotainment market. Additionally, new product launches and development of ride sharing and mobility services will act as significant market driver and hence further boost new opportunities for the market’s growth. Government mandates on telematics and e-call services will further propel the market’s growth rate and further boost more new opportunities for display unit in vehicle infotainment market.

However, high cost associated with advanced technologies and services in infotainment systems will stymie the revenue growth of display unit in vehicle infotainment market. The dearth of awareness and lack of skilled workforce will pose major challenges for the growth of display unit in vehicle infotainment market. Also, technological barriers, cybersecurity and scarcity of seamless connectivity will act as major market restrain that will further hinder the growth of display unit in vehicle infotainment market during the above mentioned forecast period.

